sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor NguoiGui as NguoiGui
actor NguoiNhan as NguoiNhan
participant Client as UngDungWeb
participant Socket as SocketService
participant Queue as RabbitMQ
participant ChatSvc as ChatService
participant MsgDb as Mongo_Message

Note over NguoiGui,MsgDb: Chặng 1 - Gửi tin nhắn thành công
NguoiGui->>Client: Nhập nội dung và bấm gửi
Client->>Socket: emit friend:send / room:send
Socket->>Queue: Publish job message
Queue->>ChatSvc: Consume job
ChatSvc->>MsgDb: Validate + lưu message
ChatSvc-->>Socket: Ack
Socket-->>NguoiNhan: Realtime tin nhắn mới
Socket-->>NguoiGui: Xác nhận gửi thành công
